# Build outputs
site/
dashboard/dist/
agent-windows/dist/
agent-windows/build/
# backend/app/static/ is committed on purpose: the Linux installer serves the
# dashboard from this prebuilt copy (install.sh does not run npm).
# installer/build/ sources (build_all.sh, winsw_templates/) are committed;
# only its staging/output artifacts are ignored.
installer/build/stage/
installer/build/dist/
installer/build/prebuilt/
*.exe
*.msi
!installer/**/*.iss

